# Development-help materials: source mirrors + reference PDFs you read while
# developing. Ignored except the in-folder convention doc. See external/README.md.
# Uses external/* (not external/) so the README exception can re-include — a
# parent dir excluded by `external/` cannot have children re-included.
external/*
!external/README.md

# Local paper projects live here as independent nested git repositories.
# Shared convention and style docs are the exceptions that live in magmaan.
papers/*
!papers/AGENTS.md
!papers/STYLE.md
!papers/CLAUDE.md

